模块 com.example.BubbleBobble
程序包 com.example.BubbleBobble.Model.User

类 UserSetting

java.lang.Object
com.example.BubbleBobble.Model.User.UserSetting
public class UserSetting extends Object
Class of UserSetting contains all the information before user starts the game, and after the game is set. UserSetting instance contains all the information, including:
  1. String Hero Color
  2. String Background Color
  3. String Difficulties
  4. int score
  5. int level
